# One still per theme for the README theme grid — same scene as the hero.
Output demo/.themes/%SUFFIX%.gif

Set Theme "%THEME%"
Set FontSize 26
Set Width 2400
Set Height 1440
Set Padding 24

Hide
Type `cd /tmp/vibin-demo && vibin . -- sleep 600`
Enter
Sleep 4s
Ctrl+A
Sleep 300ms
Type "f"
Sleep 22s
Ctrl+K
Sleep 500ms
Type "main"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2s
Type ":51"
Enter
Sleep 800ms
Type "w"
Type "w"
Type "w"
Type "e"
Sleep 1500ms
Show
Sleep 500ms
Screenshot demo/.themes/%SUFFIX%.png
